 smash-hit series</a> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/wednesday">Wednesday</a> ,</em> with <em>The Nightmare Before Christmas</em> collaborator <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burton">Tim Burton</a> serving as executive producer.</p><p> Next October, Elfman is slated to perform at the Hollywood Bowl, where he&#39;ll reprise his role as Jack Skellington for the Bowl&#39;s <em>The Nightmare Before Christmas show.</em></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/danny-elfman-accused-of-sexual-misconduct-by-second-woman-3518653">Danny Elfman accused of sexual misconduct by second woman</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
